# Machine-local package ignore list for `brew-sync` (see sources/utils.sh).
#
# Packages listed here are installed on THIS machine but intentionally kept out
# of the shared Brewfile — brew-sync will not report them as EXTRA.
#
# This file is the COMMITTED TEMPLATE. install.sh copies it to
# brew/.Brewfile.ignore (gitignored, per-machine) which stow then symlinks to
# ~/.Brewfile.ignore. Edit your local copy, never this template.
#
# One package name per line; blank lines and # comments are ignored.
#
# Example:
# android-studio
# google-drive
